metadata.name: Wish you were here
metadata.description:
Wish you were here

A beautiful Fall day in Altaussee lake in Austria, a place where time seems to pass by a little slower.

The Restaurant Seewiese is resting at the feet of the Trisselwand (1754) that runs almost 1000m from the lake
